### Iniciar MFA (SMS)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/identity/challenge/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fingerprint": "fingerprint_demo_123",
  "user": "teste@example.com"
}

### Verificar OTP
POST http://localhost:3000/api/identity/challenge/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fingerprint": "fingerprint_demo_123",
  "code": "000000"
}

### Verificar KBA (fallback)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/identity/challenge/verify-kba
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fingerprint": "fingerprint_demo_123",
  "answer1": "azul",
  "answer2": "1999"
}
